'''''Traverse Stars and Stride Cosmos''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[As Tomorrow Became Yesterday]].

==Steps==
# Negotiate the campaign and support the Astral Express
# Enter Amphoreus and locate Irontomb from within the world
# Establish contact with the outside world and coordinate with the Cosmic Alliance
# Delve into Amphoreus and explore the world within
# (Optional) Try to contact allies
# Follow the call of the prophecy to Dawncloud
# Head to the Demigod Council and witness (Trailblazer)'s awakening

